  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Add your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 18-20 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once cooked, remove the tray from the oven and set aside</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Chicken-breasts-on-baking-tray-no-foil-1699372527771-x200.jpg",
