            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is softening, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>dried basil</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1699372532951-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1699372532951-x400.jpg",
