            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion is beginning to soften, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>stock</strong> with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook for 10-15 min or until thickened slightly – this is your <strong>sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1699372535822-x200.jpg",
