            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, melt 30g <span class=\"text-purple\">[45g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[60g] </span><strong>butter</strong> in a pot over a medium heat</p><p>Once melted, add 30g<span class=\"text-purple\"> [45g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[60g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and stir with a wooden spoon for 1 min or until a sandy paste forms – this is your<strong> roux</strong></p><p>Add 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[525ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [700ml] </span><strong>milk</strong> gradually and whisk for 5-8 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains</p><p>Remove from the heat and season generously with<strong> pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> béchamel sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
