    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, remove the<strong> lasagne</strong> from the oven and leave to stand for 5 min (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Serve the<strong> chicken breast & spinach lasagne</strong> with a handful of <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
